show.title: The Natural Nurse

title: The Natural Nurse
content:
Guest: Luvcoach Bruce Starr Host Ellen Kamhi, PhD RN, www.naturalnurse.com, interviews The Luvcoach, Bruce Starr. <!--more-->  Bruce Starr is a radio and television talk show host and producer, a nationally known professional speaker and presenter on relationships who tours  America and internationally , presenting “Loveworks Weekend Relationship Workshops.
” He is the author of the book,  Bodytraders, Transforming Back From Player to Lover.
 Bruce Starr is AOL’s first Luvcouch, and interacted with over 6000 people during his 10 years in that capacity.
Bruce has helped people around the world gain a refreshing perspective about the challenges they  have in their  intimate relationships.
